{"tid":1641394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想離婚","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T13:33:07.000Z","uid":307469,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"46ca589cbcbbdd01582d6de43b02771d38afd64d","tid":1641394,"uid":307469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"坦白說！一齊左都6-7年了，<br />\n感情淡左，呢樣係真既！<br />\n自從婚後，我每日就好似做一件例行公事，每日煮飯洗衫既家庭主婦，我覺得自己想跳出呢個框框！<br />\n呢種生活其實唔係我想要！<br />\n我既性格係鐘意出去玩出去飲野，鐘意識朋友，比較外向，而佢就同我相反。<br />\n我原本以為一凹一凸既性格，可以互相填補番，但原來性格不合，就係不合！思想上，行為上，我地都唔相似。<br />\n我最近多左去約朋友食飯飲野，佢會極力阻止我，呢排出面比較危險～所以當然地佢擔心我，我好感恩，我好多謝佢！<br />\n但到我番到黎屋企，就會黑口黑面，我真係有啲受夠！<br />\n我都有陪佢架，但係我都有自己既世界！想過既生活！<br />\n為左佢，我有好多野都改變左，但原來為左別人而改變自己，係一件好辛苦既事！<br />\n咁佢冇朋友約食飯，係佢既事！咁點解我都要同佢一樣？<br />\n我相信我地之間，冇第三者存在！當然我唔知佢有冇啦～<br />\nBtw,我地之間已經好耐冇性生活！<br />\n有人講過，婚姻冇左性生活係唔健康～<br />\n但我真係唔想同佢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知佢對我好好，但我想講句「對唔住」"},{"pid":"f9d5a6c9c29369dbd9f9edc2da2779b0fba1c234","tid":1641394,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"屙屎未"},{"pid":"ef4b55cc3fe23e72c94e8c8026a1c13a0e1b2763","tid":1641394,"uid":152244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"唔中意咪離"},{"pid":"fc8d4a29e89b3ab894cfa2e6f77173ebce4d1a35","tid":1641394,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"美國國會疑似有全港警察名單<br />\n<br />\n謝sir應該已向美國篤灰 (含分析)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4662aa773d134c0bb66f09d8530e1de94c9f504b","tid":1641394,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"遠水 希望有4000和理非幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638741</a>"},{"pid":"6c536e29ef6133e3550f48d09852e37829ec08d3","tid":1641394,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"無性生活我可以幫你<br />\n又唔洗離婚既"},{"pid":"540b4718c4419e231b056b6042c339fc2b1b7575","tid":1641394,"uid":225050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"越早決定越好，拖住只會越辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819dba271c85097038387611d9c97146de9fafaa","tid":1641394,"uid":217452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"結之前又唔諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6d1090f51d6295e7b97b71032d3af0ff5d3abe","tid":1641394,"uid":196111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"如果有心想改善關係，去做吓marriage counseling, 冇心就算了"},{"pid":"f84046fb443b23daa40c5d5d8a92b5dd84ff3dc4","tid":1641394,"uid":89200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"有仔女未？"},{"pid":"f8b41fd5168d16a2f14f30e15d2d34cf09478a43","tid":1641394,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"絲打出唔出黎傾？"},{"pid":"8061f32da08ad5e13d642779fd9c9029d5e7bdc5","tid":1641394,"uid":193093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"有仔女未"},{"pid":"d8d41855acf59eeffcaa1ba43b5cf851051178f5","tid":1641394,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"我都有同樣問題，但是是男方，唔識點解決，想挽留，但成日被罵"},{"pid":"3055479ab421f812192c02402929842e299094b8","tid":1641394,"uid":307469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540b4718c4419e231b056b6042c339fc2b1b7575","tid":1641394,"uid":225050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"越早決定越好，拖住只會越辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<br />\n因為始終我都唔想拖住佢時間"},{"pid"